==Esperanto==
===Prefix===
'''ge-'''
# of both [[sexes]]; of unspecified [[sex]]
#:'''examples'''
#:*[[patroj]] ''[[fathers]]'' (''[[parents]] of unspecified sex'' in [[Riismo]]), [[gepatroj]] ''[[parent]]s of unspecified sex''.
#:*[[frato]] ''[[brother]]'' (''[[sibling]] of unspecified sex'' in [[Riismo]]), [[gefrato]] ''[[sibling]] of unspecified sex''.
====Usage note====
In [[Riism]] this prefix is rarely used, since there is little requirement for it, nouns having no implied sex unless [[-in-]] or [[-iĉ-]] are explicitly affixed.  Riist speakers use it for clarity when communicating with non-Riist speakers, in the cases of those 20 nouns that, in non-Riist Esperanto, imply a male sex, as exemplified above.

